          <%= image_tag "captions/amenities.png", class: "img-responsive caption" %>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-7" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
              <h4>MEZZANINE LEVEL</h4>

              <p>FITNESS & WEIGHT TRAINING ROOM<br>
                AEROBIC / YOGA ROOM<br>
                ICE SPA &amp; FITNESS CENTRE<br>
                MASSAGE ROOMS<br>
                RELAXING LOUNGE<br>
                SAUNA<br>
                COLD PLUNGE<br>
                STEAM ROOM<br>
                SWIMMING POOL &amp; HOT TUB</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-5" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
              <h4>SECOND LEVEL</h4>

              <p>PARTY ROOM<br>
                KITCHEN<br>
                COCKTAIL/DINING ROOM<br>
                LOUNGE<br>
                BUSINESS CENTRE<br>
                BOARD ROOM<br>
                MEETING ROOM
              </p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="row" style="padding-top: 30px;">
          <div class="col-sm-6" style="padding-right: 0;">
            <%= image_tag "building-3.jpg", class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h3> ICE OFFERS A GREEN ROOF THAT WILL IMPACT THE TORONTO SKYLINE WITH LUSH, OXYGEN CREATING LANDSCAPING,
              WHILE CREATING A CANOPY OF ORGANIC SHELTER OVER THE BUSTLING PLAZA BELOW.</h3>
